snippet.textDisplay: Thank you for recording this. As a Chinese, although I live in Switzerland, I always keep an eye on what is happening in China. It has been ridiculous and sad for me to witness the government to stick to Covid-zero policy, not mention what the authority has done to make it happen. I hope people in China can have good life as they are amazing people.
